						               													<description>La Guerre des Tuques is a team based party game where both team are in the middle of a snowball fight.&amp;#10;The goal of the game is for a team to create the largest Snow Fort while throwing SNOWBALL cards to the other players.&amp;#10;A player losing a snowball fight will receive a WOUND card that will affect him physically during the rest of the game. (example: Must now speak with its teeth clenched). Players that do not obey the wound cards will have their team lose a FORT card to the other team.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Hilarity ensues as the players try to build the biggest fort!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;From the publisher. (french version)&amp;#10;Plongez-vous dans l&amp;rsquo;univers qui a marqu&amp;eacute; plus d&amp;rsquo;une g&amp;eacute;n&amp;eacute;ration d&amp;rsquo;enfants. Cette fois-ci, incarnez un des personnages cultes du film, rassemblez-vous en deux &amp;eacute;quipes et pr&amp;eacute;parez-vous pour la bataille.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Tous les coups sont permis et les cons&amp;eacute;quences sont farfelues.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Construisez votre fort pour gagner la Guerre des Tuques.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
